Package: nginx-mainline
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: nginx, httpd, httpd-cgi
Conflicts: nginx, nginx-stable
Replaces: nginx, nginx-stable
Description: high performance web server and reverse proxy (mainline)
 nginx ("engine x") is a high performance web server, reverse proxy, and
 IMAP/POP3 proxy server. It is known for its stability, rich feature set,
 simple configuration, and low resource consumption.
 .
 This package is compiled from the nginx mainline release branch, which is
 updated roughly every one to two months and includes the latest features,
 bug fixes, and security fixes. The mainline branch always carries an odd
 minor version number (for example, 1.31.x).

Package: nginx-mainline-module-njs
Architecture: any
Depends: nginx-mainline (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: njs scripting dynamic modules for nginx (mainline)
 This package provides the njs dynamic modules (ngx_http_js_module and
 ngx_stream_js_module) for nginx. njs is a subset of the JavaScript language
 that allows extending nginx functionality in the http and stream contexts.
 .
 The modules are compiled against the matching nginx-mainline build and must
 be loaded with the load_module directive.

Package: nginx-mainline-module-otel
Architecture: any
Depends: nginx-mainline (= ${binary:Version}), opentelemetry-cpp, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenTelemetry dynamic module for nginx (mainline)
 This package provides the OpenTelemetry dynamic module (ngx_otel_module) for
 nginx. It enables distributed tracing of requests by exporting spans over
 OTLP/gRPC.
 .
 The module is compiled against the matching nginx-mainline build and must be
 loaded with the load_module directive.
